#  WELCOME TO MICCICHE CORPORATE PHOTOGRAPHY - SERVING NORTH CAROLINA SINCE
2004

Specializing in corporate and commercial photography services for executive
headshot clients, real estate industry, corporate branding, product
photography and more in Greensboro, High Point, Winston Salem and surrounding
NC Triad areas.  We also provide special event photography coverage for
functions such as award banquets, grand openings, holiday parties, golf
outings, ribbon cutting ceremonies, corporate conferences and VIP gatherings.
We have the ability to bring additional photographers and or videographers
when needed for larger events.  
  
Since 2004 Micciche Corporate Photography has documented some big events all
over the United States and have had the honor of photographing influential
people such as Maya Angelou, Herbie Hancock, Jack Nicklaus, Emmylou Harris,
Alan Alda, Tom Tillis, Renee Fleming, Daveed Diggs, Geena Davis, Roy Cooper
and Food Network Allstar Chef Jet Tila to name a few.  
  
Some of our newest corporate clients include Boom Supersonic, Syngenta,
Truist, Cone Health, Wyndham Hotels & Resorts, Toyota, Volvo, John Deere,
LabCorp, Towne Bank, Honda, UNCG, Vontier, Gilbarco, Carson Dellosa, Visa,
First Citizens Bank, United Healthcare, Merck, Almac and more.

We also specialize in high quality drone photo and video services and are
fully licensed with the FAA and available for state wide travel.  We continue
to grow our business and now offer all corporate and commercial photography
services to the Raleigh, Durham and Chapel Hill areas of North Carolina by
providing on-location service and mobile studio set up for executive headshot
projects.
